extends _layout

block title
  title Головна — NodeSchool Chernivtsi

block body
  include _header
  section.about
    .container
      .row
        .col-sm-12
          h1 About NodeSchool
      .row
        .col-sm-6
          p.lead Це оpen source воркшопи, які навчають веб-розробці.
        .col-sm-6
          p Спільнота проводить зустрічі в Чернівцях для обміну досвідом та для допомоги у проходження воркшопів.
  section.feature
    .container
      .row
        .col-sm-4.feature-item
          span.fa.fa-code.feature-item-icon
          h3 Learn Coding
          p.
            Join us and learn coding with us. You are going to learn the basics
            of Node.js. It's a plus if you know some JavaScript beforehand,
            but if not we can help you out.
        .col-sm-4.feature-item
          span.fa.fa-rocket.feature-item-icon
          h3 Self-Guided
          p.
            You will go through a set of self-paced challenges. No boring talks.
            (An occasional interesting talk is possible, though!)
            All challenges are Open Source and available online on
            nodeschool.io. This means you can continue learning after the event.
        .col-sm-4.feature-item
          span.fa.fa-heart.feature-item-icon
          h3 For Everyone
          p.
            We think coding is awesome and everyone should feel welcome at our
            event. This includes that we are expecting all participants to be
            awesome to each other and respect the Code of Conduct.
